Title: Cuci
Writer: Hans Isaac (screenplay), Hans Isaac (story), Harith Iskander (screenplay), Harith Iskander (story)
Actors: Umie Aida, Awie, Harun Salim Bachik, Elaine Daly
Plot: 4 friend who work together as a cleaner want to take a new level in their work, to clean the tallest Malaysian building, KLCC. They must compete to get the job, can they win?
